short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Change User-Agent Setting. Spoof it to the UA of Firefox, Android, Chromebook, Safari, Googlebot or a custom string.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension has been discontinued. Please install and use our new extension offering many advanced features: https://chromewebstore.google.com/detail/jkafdamincoabdjebhjmbiflploojgjf

Choose from the preset User-Agent strings, or add your own custom User-Agent string.

Available Preset UAs: Firefox on Windows, Chrome on Android & iPad, Safari (on iPhone, iPadOS/macOS), Google Bot, Chromium on Raspberry Pi and many more.

Extension by BrowserNative. Have any feedback? Email at browsernative.apps@gmail.com.
